@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Home Page";
}

<img src="~/Images/Home_Banner.jpg" alt="Banner Image" class="img-fluid rounded shadow-lg w-100" style="max-height: 500px; object-fit: cover;" />
<div class="py-3">
    <div class="text-center">
        <h1 class="display-4 mt-4 mb-2">Welcome to</h1>
        <h1 class="display-4 mb-4" style="font-family: 'Bungee Shade', cursive; color: #251605;" ">Bean Scene</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="container text-center">
        <h2 class="display-6 mb-3" style="color: #43766C;">About Us</h2>
        <p class="lead mb-3">Welcome to Bean Scene, a vibrant and welcoming family-friendly restaurant located in the heart of Sydney, Australia. Established in 2018 by two passionate brothers, James and Max Smith, Bean Scene was born out of a love for great food and a desire to create a warm community space where families and friends can gather to enjoy delicious meals together.</p>
    </div>
</div>

<div>
    <div class="container">
        <p class="lead mb-3">At Bean Scene, we take pride in our commitment to quality and affordability. Our menu features a diverse selection of dishes crafted from fresh, locally-sourced ingredients, ensuring that every meal is not only tasty but also supports our community. From hearty breakfasts to delightful dinners, each dish is prepared with care by our dedicated kitchen staff, who are passionate about creating memorable dining experiences.</p>
    </div>
</div>

<div>
    <div class="container">
        <p class="lead mb-3">Our restaurant is open all day, making it the perfect spot for any occasion, whether you’re looking for a casual breakfast, a family lunch, or a celebratory dinner. We understand the importance of special moments, which is why we offer bookings for events and parties. Our team is here to help you plan and execute your celebrations, providing tailored menus and attentive service to ensure your event is a success.</p>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="py-3">
    <div class="container">
        <p class="lead mb-3">At Bean Scene, we believe in building lasting relationships with our customers and suppliers. Our commitment to our community extends beyond the plate; we actively engage in local initiatives and support sustainable practices. Our menus reflect our dedication to quality by sourcing meat and vegetables from trusted local suppliers, ensuring that you receive the freshest and best ingredients in every bite.</p>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="py-3">
    <div class="container">
        <p class="lead mb-3">Join us at Bean Scene for an exceptional dining experience where great food, friendly service, and a sense of community come together. We invite you to be a part of our journey as we continue to grow and serve the wonderful people of Sydney.</p>
    </div>
</div>

<h2 class="text-center my-5">What Our Customers Say</h2>
