                <small>- Mark S.</small>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
            <div class="d-block w-100 p-4 text-center border rounded shadow-sm">
                <h5 class="font-weight-bold">Excellent Service!</h5>
                <p>"The staff are friendly and attentive. I always feel taken care of during my visits."</p>
                <small>- Lisa W.</small>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
            <div class="d-block w-100 p-4 text-center border rounded shadow-sm">
                <h5 class="font-weight-bold">Cozy Ambiance</h5>
                <p>"The atmosphere is so cozy and inviting. Perfect for a relaxing meal or catching up with friends."</p>
                <small>- Tom R.</small>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
            <div class="d-block w-100 p-4 text-center border rounded shadow-sm">
